lead_paragraph: Former U.S. Secretary of State and potential presidential contender Hillary Clinton said on Wednesday she supported President Barack Obama's move to establish diplomatic ties with Cuba after more than 50 years of hostile relations.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Backs Obama Move on Cuba
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Backs Obama Move on Cuba
